This is a very simple bot to point out common mistakes in writing.
It directly ties into GNU Diction (http://www.gnu.org/software/diction/).

Dependencies include:
- Perl (tested with v5.10)
- GNU Diction (tested with v1.10)
- And the following Perl modules, available from CPAN:
  - Bot::BasicBot (http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?Bot::BasicBot)
  - Moose (http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?Moose)
  - MooseX::NonMoose (http://search.cpan.org/perldoc?MooseX::NonMoose)

The code in this repo is public domain.
